Mu Rwanda hatangijwe uburyo bwo kubungabunga ibidukikije hatwera ibiti by 'imigano,  imigano miliyoni 3 <ref>Mu Rwanda hagiye kubakwa uruganda rutunganya ibikoresho mu migano - Kigali Today</ref>imaze guterwa ku nkengero z’imigezi n’ibiyaga, ku buso bwa Hegitari 2,129 , muduce dutandukanye tw'igihugu harimo umwihariko mu nkengero z'imigezi , ibiyaga, ibyuzi  harimo umugezi wa Nyabarongo,  n’Akanyaru,mu biyaga nki icyabugesera , ruhondo ,muhazi na handi , no munkengero ya pariki y'ibirunga<ref>Musanze: Imigano yitaweho yaba igisubizo ku kwangiza amashyamba - Kigali Today</ref> .

== Akamaro k'igiti cy'umugano ==
Imigano ni biti byiza  mu kubungabunga ibidukikije no mu buzima bwa burimunsi bwa muntu kuko havamo ibikoresho bitandukanya .

Imwe mu mimaro y'imigano<ref>Hatangijwe umushinga wo gutera imigano izajya ibyazwamo ibindi bikoresho - IGIHE.com</ref> :

* Ibungabunga urusobe rw'inyabuzima ni ibimera.
* Imigano ifata ubutaka mu kurwanya isuri
* Imigano ni ibiti bigira uruhare mu kurwanya imihindagurikire y;ikirere n'ibiza .

* Imigano ikorwa bimwe mukoresho byifashishwa na muntu ;urugero nkintebe ,ameza, imitako nibindi<ref>Mu Rwanda hagiye kubakwa uruganda rutunganya ibikoresho mu migano - Kigali Today</ref>....

* Imigano ikoreshwa mu kubaka amazu <ref>Menya byinshi ku kamaro k’imigano inaribwa - Kigali Today</ref>



== Umwihariko udasanzwe ku giti cy'umugano ==
[[Dosiye:Imigano ku mazi.jpg|thumb|Zimwe mu nkengero z'imigezi hateweho  ibiti by'imigano.]]
Mu Rwanda nyuma yo kubyaza inyungu igiti cy'umugano noneho hagiye guterwa imigano iribywa nk'ibiryo ,nki ibintu bitari bimenyerewe ku bazi umugano banawubyaza inyungu .Abaryi bi imigano mu bindi bihugu bavugako havamo ibiribwa bitandukanye biryoha <ref>Menya byinshi ku kamaro k’imigano inaribwa - Kigali Today</ref>.

